                    <span>Worthy theoretical reading on what C++ language is capable of and is a surprize even after years you've programmed in it. Not practical for your everyday projects; still get one and read it!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">The Loki factory pattern alone worth the price of the book</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
